                            SCPFront-JP
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p>为了能使基金会这一存在能够在一般社会中消失的同时与外界保持联络，几个前台组织被设立以及运营。从大的国际联合企业到小镇花店，规模或大或小。地域81的前台机构如下所示。</p>
<hr />
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><span style="color:green"><strong>Start-up Center &quot;Plus&quot;</strong></span></span></p>
<p>Start-up Center &quot;Plus&quot;是Plus信用金库运营的创业支援计划。旗下有诸多在不同领域出彩，拥有别样特征以及专长的潜力企业。</p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-front-jp/startup_center_plus.png" width="400px" alt="startup_center_plus.png" class="image" /></div>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-front-jp/visiting_card.png" width="400px" alt="visiting_card.png" class="image" /></div>
<blockquote>
<p>此为Start-up Center &quot;Plus&quot;旗下的林业综合研究所以及工业技术综合中心等潜力企业，但实际上大都是收容设施的伪装用前台，并以东北地方为中心展开。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<hr />
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
　<br />
<span style="font-size:130%;"><span style="color:darkorange"><strong>Sigma Creative Products Co., Ltd.</strong></span></span></p>
<p>Sigma Creative Products 股份有限公司的宗旨是活用互联网技术以此进行策划咨询，提供物流以及材料管理之类的服务。</p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-front-jp/sigma_creative_products.jpg" width="400px" alt="sigma_creative_products.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-front-jp/sigma_creative_products_semitruck.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="sigma_creative_products_semitruck.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>将SCP-███-JP送往Site-8181的伪装回收车</p>
</div>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p>Sigma Creative Products 股份有限公司实际上是专攻进行互联网监视以及隐蔽活动，异常项目的回收以及提供伪装运输车的工作。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<hr />
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><strong>SC PROPERTIES INC.</strong></span></p>
<p>SC PROPERTIES股份有限公司是从事有关酒店，商业设施，办公楼，休养别墅，住宅，停车场等开发以及开放商业务。旧称为狮子建设股份有限公司(Shishi Construction, INC.)。</p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-front-jp/sc_properties.jpg" width="300px" alt="sc_properties.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>狮子建设股份有限公司是主要以首都圈为中心，进行收容设施的伪装建设为目的，于████年被基金会秘密收购。收购后改名为SC PROPERTIES股份有限公司。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<hr />
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<div style="float:left; margin:0 2em 1em 2em; width:230px; border:0;"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-front-jp/skeptic_and_claimant_productions.jpg" width="230px" alt="skeptic_and_claimant_productions.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><span style="color:darkblue"><strong>Skeptic and Claimant Productions</strong></span></span></p>
<p>Skeptic and Claimant Productions是验证超常现象以及伪科学的日本怀疑主义论的集体。拥有包括科学家，记者，作家，资产家在内的庞大会员。</p>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<div style="float:right; margin:0 2em 1em 2em; width:230px; border:0;"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-front-jp/magazine.jpg" width="230px" alt="magazine.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<p>为了将超常现象有关的情报和调查结果公布于世，本集团会发行机关杂志『超常事件记录薄（log of extranormal events）』。该杂志把至今为止确认到的超常现象以科学的角度分析，将其最终归结于自然现象或者人为造物。</p>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Skeptic and Claimant Productions的目的是将虚拟信息和伪造故事散布至公众中。将异常的存在以及基金会活动和超常现象的痕迹在一般社会中抹去。与此同时也担任在民间招募基金会新职员等多种业务。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<hr />
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<div style="float:right; margin:0 2em 1em 2em; width:150px; border:0;"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-front-jp/souun_catalyst_partners.jpg" width="150px" alt="souun_catalyst_partners.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<br />
<span style="font-size:130%;"><span style="color:blue"><strong>Souun Catalyst Partners,INC.</strong></span></span>
<p>业云（Souun） Catalyst Partners股份有限公司是投资企业，提供股份的转让，转收，业务的转让，转收以及继承等多项服务。</p>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>业云（Souun） Catalyst Partners的目的是寻找那些无继承人的一般企业，并使其被基金会的前台企业所收购，转让和继承。也担负着使已存在前台企业的营业规模扩大，新兴前台企业的设置，GOI所持有设施的处理等多重职责。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<hr />
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><span style="color:darkgreen"><strong>Shinano Chuo Post Co., Ltd.</strong></span></span></p>
<p>信浓中央新闻社是一家总部设置在长野县的日本新闻报社，并发行信浓中央报纸。<br />
信浓中央报纸是以全国新闻为主题的普通日刊报纸。与其他的新闻报纸共享主要大事，发行量在全国新闻报纸中排在前列。</p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-front-jp/shinano_chuo_post.jpg" width="200px" alt="shinano_chuo_post.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<blockquote>
<p>信浓中央新闻社是一家利用媒体进行信息操作和加工的前台企业。所有的办公楼作为Site-81██的伪装大楼进行使用。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<hr />
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<div style="float:right; margin:0 2em 1em 2em; width:200px; border:0;"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-front-jp/sakura_conscientious_pharmaceutical.jpg" width="200px" alt="sakura_conscientious_pharmaceutical.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><span style="color:pink"><strong>Sakura Conscientious Pharmaceutical Inc.</strong></span></span></p>
<p>樱花良心制药属于可以以拥有国内最大规模的营业体系为傲的大型制药公司之一。本公司为实现制造出能治百病万能药的梦想而努力。</p>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>樱花良心制药公司主要的职责为给在医疗机关潜伏的特工提供安全屋，联络据点以及作为医疗部队的对策据点设施。为了能应对紧急呼叫所以驻扎了许多应急医疗队伍。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">　</span><br />
